OL,3,CJersey's Bailiff says cameras in
OL,4,Ccourts would show open justice
OL,6,FJersey's new Bailiff says he will
OL,7,Fbring forward a consultation on
OL,8,Fintroducing cameras in court for
OL,9,Fsentencings in significant criminal
OL,10,Fcases.
OL,12,FRobert MacRae says he wants the public
OL,13,Fto have a better understanding of the
OL,14,Fcourt's reasons for imposing the
OL,15,Fsentences that they do.
OL,17,FHe was speaking on the day he was
OL,18,Fsworn in as the island's new Bailiff -
OL,19,Fthe dual role is both Jersey's chief
OL,20,Fjudge and the President of the States
OL,21,FAssembly.
