OL,3,CJersey's Bailiff says cameras in
OL,4,Ccourts would show open justice
OL,6,FBroadcasters were first allowed to
OL,7,Ffilm sentencings in courts in England
OL,8,Fand Wales in July 2022.
OL,10,FIt has only ever involved cameras
OL,11,Ffilming the judge delivering their
OL,12,Fsentences - but the footage has been
OL,13,Fused widely in both news bulletins and
OL,14,Fwider programming.
OL,16,FBoth Jersey and Guernsey still ban
OL,17,Fcameras from Channel Island courtrooms.
