OL,3,CJersey's Bailiff says cameras in
OL,4,Ccourts would show open justice
OL,6,FHowever, Mr MacRae says he wants
OL,7,Fpeople to understand why judges impose
OL,8,Fthe sentences they do, and this could
OL,9,Fbe one way to do so.
OL,11,FHe added as Bailiff he wants to
OL,12,Feducate people, especially young
OL,13,Fpeople, about the court system in
OL,14,FJersey.
OL,16,FOne way he'll do this is through the
OL,17,Fdevelopment of an outreach project to
OL,18,Fgo into all secondary schools, to
OL,19,Fteach pupils about the role of the
OL,20,FBailiff and his office.
