OL,3,CJersey's Bailiff says cameras in
OL,4,Ccourts would show open justice
OL,6,FMr MacRae said: "I want to ensure the
OL,7,Frole is preserved, that it is a role
OL,8,Fthat commands the respect of the
OL,9,Fpeople of Jersey, and as my
OL,10,Fpredecessor did I will do my best to
OL,11,Fensure the role is opened up further
OL,12,Fto people."
OL,14,FHe added: "I want to help people to
OL,15,Funderstand the work of the Bailiff, so
OL,16,Fthey understand the work of the courts
OL,17,Fand understand that in the criminal
OL,18,Fsphere, we will do our best to ensure
OL,19,Fthat victims and witnesses are treated
OL,20,Fkindly by the courts."
