OL,3,CJersey's Bailiff says cameras in
OL,4,Ccourts would show open justice
OL,6,FWhen asked if he had a message for the
OL,7,Fpeople of Jersey, he said: "The Office
OL,8,Fof Bailiff is here for everyone. On
OL,9,Fthe occasions that the Bailiff speaks
OL,10,Fto the island - in celebration on
OL,11,FLiberation Day, or in remembrance on
OL,12,FRemembrance Sunday, or in times of
OL,13,Fnational mourning after the death of a
OL,14,Fsovereign, or coronation or a Royal
OL,15,FVisit - when the Bailiff speaks, I
OL,16,Fhope people know it's for everyone and
OL,17,Fto everyone, regardless of their age,
OL,18,Fregardless of where they were born and
OL,19,Fregardless of their faith."
